Nowadays, social media is very popular, almost everyone who has a smart phone might has social media application. One of the most popular applications is Instagram, in my society Instagram is the most popular application.
According to Sheldon and Bryant (2016) quantity of time spend editing photos for Instagram was connected to the level of narcissism. Dion (2016) states that people who followed many celebrities on Instagram may experience a reduce in life satisfaction. I believe that Instagram has a positive side. Instagram may be used to marketing. My friend is an owner of clothes shop, she advertising and selling on Instagram.
To conclude, social media is so popular and it has positive and negative sides, it depends on the way we use it.